jphase.fit

Class MomentsACPH2Fit

  • java.lang.Object
    • jphase.fit.ContPhaseFitter
      • jphase.fit.MomentsContPhaseFitter
        • jphase.fit.MomentsACPH2Fit
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PhaseFitter

    public class MomentsACPH2Fit
extends MomentsContPhaseFitter
    This class implements the moment-matching method proposed by Telek and Heindl in "Matching Moments for Acyclic discrete and continuous Phase-Type distributions of Second order", 2002. The method returns a continuous Phase-type variable.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Juan F. Perez
